  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/ImageIO\/kCGImagePropertyMakerNikonShootingMode\ncrawled: 2025-12-13T00:33:08Z\n---\n\n# kCGImagePropertyMakerNikonShootingMode\n\n**Global Variable**\n\nThe shooting mode.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nlet kCGImagePropertyMakerNikonShootingMode: CFString\n```\n\n## Program Settings\n\n- **kCGImagePropertyMakerNikonISOSetting**: The ISO setting.\n- **kCGImagePropertyMakerNikonISOSelection**: The ISO selection.\n- **kCGImagePropertyMakerNikonColorMode**: The color mode.\n- **kCGImagePropertyMakerNikonQuality**: The quality setting.\n- **kCGImagePropertyMakerNikonWhiteBalanceMode**: The white balance mode.\n- **kCGImagePropertyMakerNikonSharpenMode**: The sharpening mode.\n- **kCGImagePropertyMakerNikonFocusMode**: The focus mode.\n- **kCGImagePropertyMakerNikonFlashSetting**: The flash setting.\n- **kCGImagePropertyMakerNikonImageAdjustment**: The image adjustment setting.\n- **kCGImagePropertyMakerNikonDigitalZoom**: The digital zoom setting.\n- **kCGImagePropertyMakerNikonShutterCount**: The number of times the shutter has been actuated.\n- **kCGImagePropertyMakerNikonFlashExposureComp**: The flash exposure compensation.\n- **kCGImagePropertyMakerNikonFocusDistance**: The focus distance.\n\n",
